{"tid":1607452,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"灣仔大廈內檢可製汽油彈物料 警方拘兩學生在內5男子","createTime":"2019-09-30T23:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T00:33:27.000Z","uid":29675,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"15db2c85f169967ff7fc5cb19934ac2945c02e2b","tid":1607452,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T23:46:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483513-20191001.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483513-20191001.htm&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdUcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=519b1428\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483513-20191001.htm&h=2ebb6f13\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483513-20191001.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n2019-10-01 HKT 07:40<br />\n<br />\n警方在灣仔駱克道一幢大廈內拘捕5名男子，指他們涉嫌串謀藏有及製造攻擊性武器， 在單位內檢獲玻璃樽、天拿水、白電油、鎂粉、鋁粉等可製作汽油彈的物料，亦搜出防毒面罩及口罩等，警方相信檢獲物品與近月的暴力事件有關。被捕5人年齡介乎17至31歲，包括兩名學生。<br />\n<br />\n商業罪案調查科警司洪毅表示，根據線報，昨晚10時許到駱克道一幢大廈調查，在大堂拘捕兩名男子。調查期間，在一個單位拍門，由於無人應門，警方破門進入，當時單位內有3名男子，其中兩人爬出窗外，消防及談判專家到場，經游說後到將兩人帶回單位內。<br />\n<br />\n洪毅表示，在公眾地方投擲汽油彈屬嚴重罪行，相當於縱火，一經定罪，最高可被判終身監禁。"},{"pid":"1bc402bc1994708eedb686c964de6bfc64075a69","tid":1607452,"uid":64345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T23:47:56.000Z","msg":"學生要做到咁，你地唔係仲唔出呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a98655192fddb96e8563cb0865d10e5ab7805f","tid":1607452,"uid":266672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T23:48:54.000Z","msg":"頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d61dbbacc7a5b29a8190364d83c88aeded1d125","tid":1607452,"uid":158889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T23:50:12.000Z","msg":"點解學生咁做 咪就係你班仆街無人帶囉 一人一支都幾十萬支啦屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1baedb52e58318468f5535d33474605dadc6c2","tid":1607452,"uid":67509,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T23:51:32.000Z","msg":"鄰居篤灰？<br />\n如果成班男人黑衫捧住堆野入屋，真係好易俾人篤"},{"pid":"a3db1fa30c5ad4a8d71133139e7c5efcd90e04ac","tid":1607452,"uid":136590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T23:51:35.000Z","msg":"公安條例必須廢除<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a49029c29d56a8b93e1497403508b614f36bd0","tid":1607452,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T23:59:13.000Z","msg":"又黎呢招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要整洗撚集中咩"},{"pid":"b7036cedab6c6190002621b0380983ceee8baa1c","tid":1607452,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T00:00:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff8a37cf1d8a96a2e367f7052350c79081996e60","tid":1607452,"uid":76776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T00:04:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f586f6a0698a03ce092a8073cb40e5549cef5b0","tid":1607452,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T00:07:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96584c86947f7ef17ac6430ff0dadab82a5ce79d","tid":1607452,"uid":302165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T00:27:59.000Z","msg":"遮骨造箭，一把咳鉗，好易拆除，用單車胎，<br />\n丫义彈射，射程十米，多試幾次，練習準繩，<br />\n遮骨咳尖，遮骨有坑，快速放血，切勿使用！<br />\n水馬陣內，黑狗開槍，隔馬彈射，以武止暴！"},{"pid":"70bd0d87b90ed86576b05e7cae8faeb9f99651a5","tid":1607452,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T00:31:40.000Z","msg":"出la!!!"},{"pid":"b22c745a3b72cff2b80165661ffbdf12f5eff68a","